Workspace attach/routing/session/sync correctness plus global plugin adapters.

Adds the workspace correctness slice needed by kfactory:

  - opencode attach --workspace propagates through tui() into SDKProvider and ProjectProvider.
  - validateSession honors the selected workspace.
  - workspace-routing middleware reads x-opencode-workspace for all methods, not only ?workspace=.
  - Session.list and Session.listGlobal use workspace_id as the primary scope when workspaceID is explicit.
  - /experimental/session forwards ?workspace= into Session.listGlobal.
  - /sync/start?workspace= targets the exact workspace after restart.
  - plugin workspace adapters register globally and lookup falls back to ProjectID.global while preserving project-specific overrides.

This patch intentionally does not include Bearer auth plumbing; see opencode-static-bearer.patch. The local stack applies that patch first, so the attach.ts option-chain hunk is stack-positioned after `--bearer`. This patch also does not include kfactory auth-cache refresh glue; see opencode-kfactory-refresh.patch.

